Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:19.94,gogo2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HD554E9&\fad(200,200)\pos(517,322)}{\bord2}{\fs20}真唯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:19.72,gogo2,,0000,0000,0000,,真唯你会怎么下呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:21.57,gogo2,,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.56,0:22:24.46,gogo2,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么想要下在那里呢？
